{"tag":"section","attrib":{"id":"id77dd0134-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5","identifier":"/us/usc/t16/s460gg–1"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"460gg–1"},"text":"§ 460gg–1.","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Wilderness designation","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"id77dd0135-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5","identifier":"/us/usc/t16/s460gg–1/a"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"a"},"text":"(a)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Map designation","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"The lands depicted as the “Hells Canyon Wilderness” on the map referred to in ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t16/s460gg/b"},"text":"section 460gg(b) of this title","children":[],"tail":" are hereby designated as wilderness."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"id77dd0136-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5","identifier":"/us/usc/t16/s460gg–1/b"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"b"},"text":"(b)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Application of Wilderness Act","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"The wilderness designated by this subchapter shall be administered by the Secretary in accordance with the provisions of this subchapter or in accordance with the provisions of the Wilderness Act [","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t16/s1131"},"text":"16 U.S.C. 1131","children":[],"tail":" et seq.], whichever is the more restrictive, except that any reference in such provisions of the Wilderness Act to the effective date of that Act shall be deemed to be a reference to the effective date of this subchapter. The provisions of section 460gg–6(b) and "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t16/s460gg–8"},"text":"section 460gg–8 of this title","children":[],"tail":" shall apply to the wilderness. The Secretary shall make such boundary revisions to the wilderness as may be necessary due to the exercise of his authority under subsection 3(b) of this Act."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"sourceCredit","attrib":{"id":"id77dd0137-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5"},"text":"(","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/94/199/s2"},"text":"Pub. L. 94–199, § 2","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1975-12-31"},"text":"Dec. 31, 1975","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/89/1117"},"text":"89 Stat. 1117","children":[],"tail":".)"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"notes","attrib":{"type":"uscNote","id":"id77dd0138-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"editorialNotes","id":"id77dd0139-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"b","attrib":{},"text":"Editorial Notes","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"referencesInText","id":"id77dd013a-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"References in Text","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"This subchapter, referred to in subsec. (b), was in the original “this Act”, which is ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/94/199"},"text":"Pub. L. 94–199","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1975-12-31"},"text":"Dec. 31, 1975","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/89/1117"},"text":"89 Stat. 1117","children":[],"tail":", which enacted sections 460gg to 460gg–13 of this title, amended sections 1274 and 1276 of this title, and enacted provisions set out as notes under sections 460gg and 1274 of this title."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"The Wilderness Act, referred to in subsec. (b), is ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/88/577"},"text":"Pub. L. 88–577","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1964-09-03"},"text":"Sept. 3, 1964","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/78/890"},"text":"78 Stat. 890","children":[],"tail":", which is classified generally to chapter 23 (§ 1131 et seq.) of this title. For complete classification of this Act to the Code, see Short Title note set out under "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t16/s1131"},"text":"section 1131 of this title","children":[],"tail":" and Tables."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"The effective date of the Wilderness Act, referred to in subsec. (b), means ","children":[{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1964-09-03"},"text":"Sept. 3, 1964","children":[],"tail":", the date of enactment of "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/88/577"},"text":"Pub. L. 88–577","children":[],"tail":", which enacted chapter 23 of this title."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"The effective date of this subchapter, referred to in subsec. (b), means ","children":[{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1975-12-31"},"text":"Dec. 31, 1975","children":[],"tail":", the date of enactment of "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/94/199"},"text":"Pub. L. 94–199","children":[],"tail":"."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Subsection 3(b) of this Act, referred to in subsec. (b), is subsec. 3(b) of ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/94/199"},"text":"Pub. L. 94–199","children":[],"tail":", which is set out as a note under "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t16/s1274"},"text":"section 1274 of this title","children":[],"tail":"."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null}
